{"tid":175504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱落街場 有條死mk帶條女黎睇波","createTime":"2017-03-27T14:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T07:13:30.000Z","uid":4492,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99be4f7da1f3b637b93a67fbd0b403a7850d6535","tid":175504,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"一開始我係咁對住佢條女個方向射波<br />\n又喺條女面前係咁插花扭水樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到落場我又係咁用skill move撚鳩條mk仔<br />\n有一下我rainbow fake完佢之後<br />\n條mk仔一肘批落黎<br />\n仲要打到我牙都甩埋<br />\n最後我一路跑住走<br />\n一路叫佢咪撚走我買完野飲返黎你就知死<br />\n結果我拎住隻牙返咗屋企就冇返到球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c250c849b3f054a09a3e6436912403881ef30672","tid":175504,"uid":41614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:01:44.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e6c6b558b2ebc78f90191efa54f7414d37eaa4","tid":175504,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"邊個場，我幫您拎返佢隻牙"},{"pid":"41e727489e4871b9623c581de60820b6871d8058","tid":175504,"uid":28041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"Cosb做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56958f7f088ba03583c7456a12e6aa34dbe4c80","tid":175504,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"崩牙狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9789685fe354661773cdcd300d8513584923231","tid":175504,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c53aba1442387c75e9426d510f4f333530e00530